#: ../../../release/1.10.4-notes.rst:3
msgid "NumPy 1.10.4 Release Notes"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release/1.10.4-notes.rst:5
msgid ""
"This release is a bugfix source release motivated by a segfault regression. "
"No windows binaries are provided for this release, as there appear to be "
"bugs in the toolchain we use to generate those files. Hopefully that problem "
"will be fixed for the next release. In the meantime, we suggest using one of "
"the providers of windows binaries."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release/1.10.4-notes.rst:12
msgid "Compatibility notes"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release/1.10.4-notes.rst:14
msgid ""
"The trace function now calls the trace method on subclasses of ndarray, "
"except for matrix, for which the current behavior is preserved. This is to "
"help with the units package of AstroPy and hopefully will not cause problems."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release/1.10.4-notes.rst:20
msgid "Issues Fixed"
msgstr ""

